{
  "stem": "893.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And while we were there, we were-- he told us that the night-- last night, he was listening to Radio Moscow, the short-wave radio, and they announced that this native city was liberated.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was still afraid, since we were maybe 50 miles away from that city, or maybe less than 50 miles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were afraid maybe they are still in retreat, and we-- we might be walking into their hands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we stayed up another week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So did they.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then-- then January, the first week, just after Christmas-- I believe-- the reason I know it was after Christmas before-- because for Christmas, the villagers gave us a-- a chicken for Christmas.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't pay for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They gave it to us as a present, a Christmas present.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't even know how to eat it, how to cook it, so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We came-- we came down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we-- we were told that the Germans-- there are no Germans in-- in the next city, in Obysovce, and it's safe for us to come down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We stayed there for a couple of days, then they took us by wagon to the city of Obysovce.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There, we-- we came by-- by wagon again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We hitched a ride.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We wanted to hitch a ride back to our hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we hitched some ride and we walked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Finally, I believe, in a couple of days-- it took us two days to get to our home city-- we came to the city.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The streets were covered with snow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was like a ghost town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You didn't see any person on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The men were taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I guess they took them to the trenches or whatever they're needed for.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
